1
00:00:00,770 --> 00:00:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell?!</font>

2
00:00:02,730 --> 00:00:05,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could something like this stand?!</font>

3
00:00:05,760 --> 00:00:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chiyo?</font>

4
00:00:06,990 --> 00:00:09,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe it...</font>

5
00:00:09,420 --> 00:00:11,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could this have been
 going on all this time?</font>

6
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll never let it go...</font>

7
00:00:14,490 --> 00:00:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#484d50"><b>Uniform Point Deductions for Female Applicants:
Nitto Medical University Accused of Arbitrary Manipulation</b></font></font></font></font>

8
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never! Not ever!</font>

9
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#3b3132">Journal with Witch</font></font></font></font>

10
00:01:59,550 --> 00:02:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font face="Georgia"><font color="#ffffff">Episode 11\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h<font size="18">Set Free</font></font></font></font></font>

11
00:02:15,490 --> 00:02:18,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morimoto's absent again?</font>

12
00:02:18,430 --> 00:02:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean Chiyo?</font>

13
00:02:19,810 --> 00:02:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been meaning 
to give this back to her.</font>

14
00:02:21,740 --> 00:02:23,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font color="#ab3f46">Fifty People</font></font></font>

15
00:02:24,740 --> 00:02:26,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You try texting her?</font>

16
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:27,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know her number.</font>

17
00:02:28,530 --> 00:02:30,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We only really talk here.</font>

18
00:02:31,260 --> 00:02:33,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been exchanging books.</font>

19
00:02:33,850 --> 00:02:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you hear what happened last week?</font>

20
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:40,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, isn't this cute?</font>

21
00:02:40,690 --> 00:02:43,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like something you'd like.</font>

22
00:02:43,190 --> 00:02:44,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that supposed to mean?</font>

23
00:02:45,510 --> 00:02:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's cute.</font>

24
00:02:48,140 --> 00:02:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="10"><font color="#808581">Library</font></font></font></font>

25
00:02:57,100 --> 00:02:58,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, right!</font>

26
00:02:58,140 --> 00:03:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're good! You're good, I tell you!</font>

27
00:03:03,150 --> 00:03:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did Shinozaki ignore you just now?</font>

28
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up with that?</font>

29
00:03:06,470 --> 00:03:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows?</font>

30
00:03:08,130 --> 00:03:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard he and Hashiba broke up.</font>

31
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't care less.</font>

32
00:03:12,510 --> 00:03:13,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ouch.</font>

33
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:17,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chiyo was supposed to go 
into medical school, so...</font>

34
00:03:17,580 --> 00:03:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyways, now you know what happened.</font>

35
00:03:20,770 --> 00:03:22,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it broke her.</font>

36
00:03:22,530 --> 00:03:24,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She hasn't been to school since.</font>

37
00:03:26,380 --> 00:03:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want me to give you her number?</font>

38
00:03:28,340 --> 00:03:31,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh, sure.</font>

39
00:03:31,930 --> 00:03:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Told ya!</font>

40
00:03:33,510 --> 00:03:34,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ack!</font>

41
00:03:35,100 --> 00:03:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch it.</font>

42
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You good?</font>

43
00:03:38,530 --> 00:03:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah.</font>

44
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apologize.</font>

45
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

46
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:43,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said apologize to her.</font>

47
00:03:43,940 --> 00:03:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on, Takumi, did you just go "ack"?</font>

48
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way. Who really says that?</font>

49
00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up and apologize already.</font>

50
00:03:51,070 --> 00:03:53,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get over yourselves.</font>

51
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever. My bad.</font>

52
00:03:56,990 --> 00:03:59,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like they don't know 
how to say sorry.</font>

53
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So annoying.</font>

54
00:04:02,850 --> 00:04:05,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? You're quitting? Why?</font>

55
00:04:07,270 --> 00:04:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're running away?</font>

56
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that all baseball meant to you?</font>

57
00:04:12,210 --> 00:04:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what?</font>

58
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:17,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been picked on, 
punched in the stomach,</font>

59
00:04:17,740 --> 00:04:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">treated like a gofer, 
and forced to grovel.</font>

60
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you expect me to just take it?</font>

61
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that what baseball should mean to me?</font>

62
00:04:28,150 --> 00:04:29,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later.</font>

63
00:04:43,510 --> 00:04:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="16"><font face="Arial"><font color="#67645e">Band Club</font></font></font></font>

64
00:04:43,510 --> 00:04:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="20"><font face="Impact"><font color="#edebe9">Auditioning for vocals</font></font></font></font>

65
00:04:46,930 --> 00:04:49,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How have you been? Anything new?</font>

66
00:04:50,380 --> 00:04:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm... Not really, I guess.</font>

67
00:04:54,380 --> 00:04:54,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

68
00:04:55,260 --> 00:04:59,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know how your leg twitches 
while you're asleep?</font>

69
00:04:59,220 --> 00:05:01,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, sure do.</font>

70
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet that's—</font>

71
00:05:02,810 --> 00:05:07,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just wanted you to like me, Natsume-san.</i></font>

72
00:05:07,340 --> 00:05:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a void of a person.</font>

73
00:05:09,770 --> 00:05:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

74
00:05:10,990 --> 00:05:13,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up with this guy?</font>

75
00:05:13,810 --> 00:05:14,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

76
00:05:15,220 --> 00:05:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I meant the TV. 
You're watching it, aren't you?</font>

77
00:05:17,930 --> 00:05:20,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but I didn't think you were.</font>

78
00:05:20,050 --> 00:05:21,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was peeking out of one eye.</font>

79
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:25,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, you forgot your journal today.</font>

80
00:05:25,550 --> 00:05:27,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah.</font>

81
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:30,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw you actually closed 
it for a change.</font>

82
00:05:30,610 --> 00:05:32,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It actually made me a little sentimental.</font>

83
00:05:32,670 --> 00:05:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Why?</font>

84
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is so stupid.</font>

85
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:38,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of a plot twist is that?</font>

86
00:05:38,260 --> 00:05:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}But you never noticed me.</i></font>

87
00:05:38,260 --> 00:05:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A void of a person...</i></font>

88
00:05:40,730 --> 00:05:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="18"><font color="#74797c">Void (pronounced <i>voyd</i>)</font></font></font></font>

89
00:05:40,730 --> 00:05:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="18"><font color="#74797c">Noun; adjectival verb</font></font></font></font>

90
00:05:40,730 --> 00:05:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="15"><font color="#74797c">To be empty or contain nothing,
as in "a boundless void of space."</font></font></font></font>

91
00:05:40,730 --> 00:05:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="15"><font color="#74797c">To be meaningless and of little substance or value, as in "a void 
opinion merely echoing others' sentiments" or "days of void."</font></font></font></font>

92
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:46,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that for? Modern Japanese?</font>

93
00:05:46,810 --> 00:05:50,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no. It's just my personal notebook.</font>

94
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:53,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a collection of my aunt's trash talk.</font>

95
00:05:53,550 --> 00:05:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Her trash talk?</font>

96
00:05:56,540 --> 00:05:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I see?</font>

97
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, sure.</font>

98
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does your aunt talk that much smack?</font>

99
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:04,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not a ton, but it gets pretty 
spicy when she does.</font>

100
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#6a6657">Inane
<font size="18">To be shallow without knowledge or thought</font></font></font></font>

101
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#6a6657">Evil</font></font></font>

102
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Inane: To be shallow without 
knowledge or thought."</font>

103
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez. Harsh much?</font>

104
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Evil"? That's hilarious.</font>

105
00:06:14,530 --> 00:06:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When would you ever need to say that?</font>

106
00:06:16,380 --> 00:06:18,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said it while watching the news.</font>

107
00:06:18,140 --> 00:06:20,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474541">Impudent
<font size="18">\hTo be unabashed...</font></font></font></font>

108
00:06:18,150 --> 00:06:20,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see... "Impudent."</font>

109
00:06:20,050 --> 00:06:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Folly."</font>

110
00:06:20,150 --> 00:06:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474541">Folly
<font size="18">To be foolish...</font></font></font></font>

111
00:06:21,250 --> 00:06:22,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Cowardice."</font>

112
00:06:21,270 --> 00:06:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474541">Cowardice
<font size="18">\hTo avoid being open and fair...</font></font></font></font>

113
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:24,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474541">Benighted</font></font></font>

114
00:06:22,470 --> 00:06:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Benighted."</font>

115
00:06:23,570 --> 00:06:24,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that mean?</font>

116
00:06:24,870 --> 00:06:26,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't remember.</font>

117
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:29,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Escapist, deceitful, villainous..."</font>

118
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:33,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, this is a whole 
treasure trove of trash talk.</font>

119
00:06:34,910 --> 00:06:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="12"><font color="#74797c">Wretched (pronounced <i>retch-ed</i>)</font></font></font></font>

120
00:06:34,910 --> 00:06:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="12"><font color="#74797c">Adjective</font></font></font></font>

121
00:06:34,910 --> 00:06:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="9"><font color="#74797c">To possess ugly features. The state of possessing a nasty heart
or acting on meanness, as in "a wretched battle."</font></font></font></font>

122
00:06:35,410 --> 00:06:36,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just remembered another one.</font>

123
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:38,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474541">Wretched</font></font></font>

124
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ooh, I wanna hear.</font>

125
00:06:39,350 --> 00:06:40,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wretched!</font>

126
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:43,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'd die if someone 
ever called me that.</font>

127
00:06:43,810 --> 00:06:45,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stuff like wretched or a void.</font>

128
00:06:45,990 --> 00:06:47,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know, right?</font>

129
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:52,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474541">Void
<font size="18">\hTo have little value or content</font></font></font></font>

130
00:06:50,990 --> 00:06:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

131
00:06:52,620 --> 00:06:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess what, Dad?</font>

132
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:57,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom keeps bugging me about my hair.</font>

133
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:58,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All because I got it cut.</font>

134
00:06:58,930 --> 00:07:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just looks too much 
like a boy's haircut.</font>

135
00:07:03,370 --> 00:07:05,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hear that, Dad?</font>

136
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not listening!</font>

137
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom apparently doesn't like my hair.</font>

138
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... right.</font>

139
00:07:16,030 --> 00:07:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, just do what you want to do.</font>

140
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as it's within reason, I guess.</font>

141
00:07:35,930 --> 00:07:36,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gone...</i></font>

142
00:07:39,110 --> 00:07:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're both gone.</i></font>

143
00:07:41,580 --> 00:07:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Forever.</i></font>

144
00:07:44,610 --> 00:07:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had such a weird dream yesterday.</font>

145
00:07:47,380 --> 00:07:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Like what?</font>

146
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning.</font>

147
00:07:49,610 --> 00:07:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hey, Mori-chan! Mor...</font>

148
00:07:51,110 --> 00:07:52,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What were you saying?</font>

149
00:07:51,610 --> 00:07:52,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...ning?</font>

150
00:07:52,530 --> 00:07:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Right, so there's this Samoyed...</font>

151
00:07:54,390 --> 00:07:55,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Samoyed?</font>

152
00:07:55,110 --> 00:07:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's a breed of dog. 
They're, like, white and fluffy.</font>

153
00:07:55,110 --> 00:07:56,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look! Look at that!</font>

154
00:07:56,570 --> 00:07:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

155
00:07:57,380 --> 00:07:59,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? Right there!</font>

156
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Oh, I think I know what 
you're talking about.</font>

157
00:08:00,890 --> 00:08:01,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

158
00:08:01,930 --> 00:08:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all you have to say?!</font>

159
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:07,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you, I'm not talking 
romance with you.</font>

160
00:08:07,260 --> 00:08:09,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, please! Let's talk romance!</font>

161
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speaking of, it's almost Valentine's.</font>

162
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you doing anything, Emiri?</font>

163
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have a Valentine? Well?</font>

164
00:08:16,300 --> 00:08:17,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

165
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll give you some friendship 
chocolates again.</font>

166
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

167
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna do something for Valentine's too.</font>

168
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about Makio-san?</font>

169
00:08:26,330 --> 00:08:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should give her some chocolate.</font>

170
00:08:29,350 --> 00:08:32,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I doubt she cares about that stuff at all.</font>

171
00:08:36,660 --> 00:08:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's something to consider given 
that it takes place at school.</font>

172
00:08:40,750 --> 00:08:44,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have to make a decision 
by the end of the year.</font>

173
00:08:44,970 --> 00:08:48,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I never return
 the favor with things like this.</font>

174
00:08:48,410 --> 00:08:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, don't mention it. I hope you like it.</font>

175
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you buy chocolate this time of year?</font>

176
00:08:54,170 --> 00:08:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to, but I can't handle crowds.</font>

177
00:08:56,190 --> 00:08:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makes sense.</font>

178
00:08:57,800 --> 00:09:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although, my niece mentioned not 
having anyone to give chocolates to.</font>

179
00:09:04,500 --> 00:09:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How old is she again?</font>

180
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Almost in her second year of high school.</font>

181
00:09:08,890 --> 00:09:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She loves talking about stuff like that.</font>

182
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's quite exhausting, actually.</font>

183
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's good inspiration.</font>

184
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:21,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm making chocolates 
for my childhood friend.</font>

185
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you two going out?!</font>

186
00:09:23,950 --> 00:09:25,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, nothing like that.</font>

187
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:28,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get something for White Day in return.</font>

188
00:09:28,620 --> 00:09:30,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's a fair trade.</font>

189
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, man, I'm so jealous!</font>

190
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop shaking the desk.</font>

191
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want me to make you some too?</font>

192
00:09:37,430 --> 00:09:38,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I expect payback on White Day.</font>

193
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

194
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:42,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I told you, stop shaking the desk!</font>

195
00:09:43,300 --> 00:09:44,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you get anything?</font>

196
00:09:44,730 --> 00:09:47,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some tea. I saw the limited edition 
tag and couldn't help myself.</font>

197
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:51,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So if I got you tea as a gift,
 would you enjoy that?</font>

198
00:09:51,950 --> 00:09:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm pretty particular.</font>

199
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if it's the basic kind, sure, I guess.</font>

200
00:09:57,320 --> 00:10:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured. I could never bring myself 
to ask in case you thought it was stupid.</font>

201
00:10:02,850 --> 00:10:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad I finally did.</font>

202
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:09,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, does your job let you
out and about during the day?</font>

203
00:10:09,580 --> 00:10:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure it does. I'm on my 
lunch break right now.</font>

204
00:10:13,890 --> 00:10:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's 3 PM.</font>

205
00:10:15,350 --> 00:10:17,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. Poor me, right?</font>

206
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:33,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want some?</font>

207
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:37,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I was just admiring
 how you savor every bite.</font>

208
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a bit embarrassing 
to be stared at like that.</font>

209
00:10:41,390 --> 00:10:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spring can't come fast enough.</font>

210
00:10:44,010 --> 00:10:45,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you even listening?</font>

211
00:10:49,710 --> 00:10:51,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would've thought...</font>

212
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would've thought we'd be able 
to eat together like this again?</font>

213
00:10:57,750 --> 00:10:59,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I certainly didn't a year ago.</font>

214
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:01,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

215
00:11:02,470 --> 00:11:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a year already...</font>

216
00:11:04,690 --> 00:11:06,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rather, it's only been a year.</font>

217
00:11:08,790 --> 00:11:09,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

218
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

219
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

220
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:14,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Asa-chan?</font>

221
00:11:15,940 --> 00:11:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haven't seen her.</font>

222
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't do Monday. 
I have to make chocolates then.</font>

223
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:24,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean for me?</font>

224
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:26,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="16"><font face="Arial"><font color="#4d4737">Band Club</font></font></font></font>

225
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:26,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="20"><font face="Impact"><font color="#d5d6d1">Auditioning for vocals</font></font></font></font>

226
00:11:24,950 --> 00:11:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get too excited. 
They're for my friends.</font>

227
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll give you any leftovers.</font>

228
00:11:29,290 --> 00:11:30,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice!</font>

229
00:11:31,290 --> 00:11:32,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It makes you that happy, huh?</font>

230
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:33,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait.</font>

231
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:35,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever you say.</font>

232
00:11:37,420 --> 00:11:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep quiet.</font>

233
00:11:39,130 --> 00:11:41,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Sorry.</font>

234
00:11:43,610 --> 00:11:45,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here. For you.</font>

235
00:11:45,610 --> 00:11:47,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From Kasamachi-kun.</font>

236
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chocolate!</font>

237
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow, my eardrums.</font>

238
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This one's yours.</font>

239
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This one's mine.</font>

240
00:11:53,830 --> 00:11:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And these are from my editor.</font>

241
00:11:55,530 --> 00:11:56,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can share them.</font>

242
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:01,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're that excited?</font>

243
00:12:01,090 --> 00:12:02,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These aren't the same size!</font>

244
00:12:02,660 --> 00:12:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He played favorites, apparently.</font>

245
00:12:06,950 --> 00:12:08,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you?</font>

246
00:12:08,580 --> 00:12:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you give him anything?</font>

247
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

248
00:12:12,460 --> 00:12:16,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I gave him 
a good book last week.</font>

249
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That has nothing to do with Valentine's.</font>

250
00:12:18,580 --> 00:12:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't expect any typical 
feelings or habits out of me.</font>

251
00:12:24,730 --> 00:12:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're unapologetically 
admitting that now?</font>

252
00:12:27,610 --> 00:12:30,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not exactly. I just know myself.</font>

253
00:12:35,140 --> 00:12:38,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like I'm the only person 
in the world who's not in love.</font>

254
00:12:41,620 --> 00:12:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa, not everyone has to fall in love.</font>

255
00:12:47,700 --> 00:12:50,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's no sign of unhappiness, either.</font>

256
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:52,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're lying!</font>

257
00:12:52,110 --> 00:12:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the truth.</font>

258
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are people like that.</font>

259
00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:58,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People who don't need romance.</font>

260
00:12:59,730 --> 00:13:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's got nothing to do with me.</font>

261
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course it does.</font>

262
00:13:04,970 --> 00:13:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There isn't a single thing in this world
completely irrelevant to you.</font>

263
00:13:08,700 --> 00:13:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the very least, you could take comfort 
in the fact that you're not alone, right?</font>

264
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:17,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't get anything you're saying at all.</font>

265
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then think harder.</font>

266
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:21,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

267
00:13:21,330 --> 00:13:23,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said to think harder.</font>

268
00:13:24,220 --> 00:13:27,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know Makio-chan, you're just...</font>

269
00:13:27,330 --> 00:13:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

270
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:30,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, never mind.</font>

271
00:13:31,300 --> 00:13:32,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna go change.</font>

272
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, you think way too much.</font>

273
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, you're too sensitive.</font>

274
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you, conceited?</font>

275
00:13:51,180 --> 00:13:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I am.</font>

276
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000">Journal with Witch</font></font></font></font>

277
00:13:58,410 --> 00:13:59,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Takumi.</font>

278
00:14:02,980 --> 00:14:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know the deal.</font>

279
00:14:05,100 --> 00:14:07,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kan-chan! You're the best!</font>

280
00:14:07,140 --> 00:14:09,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep your voice down.</font>

281
00:14:12,230 --> 00:14:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

282
00:14:13,510 --> 00:14:15,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't forget next month.</font>

283
00:14:17,990 --> 00:14:20,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, is Morimoto-san absent again?</font>

284
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:21,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like it.</font>

285
00:14:22,130 --> 00:14:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will she even make it to the next grade?</font>

286
00:14:24,290 --> 00:14:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure she will. She's top of the class.</font>

287
00:14:26,880 --> 00:14:28,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you see the news?</font>

288
00:14:28,620 --> 00:14:32,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About the university docking 
points from female applicants?</font>

289
00:14:32,490 --> 00:14:34,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes me so mad!</font>

290
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:36,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what she'll be like
 when she's back.</font>

291
00:14:36,510 --> 00:14:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We probably shouldn't bring it up.</font>

292
00:14:40,690 --> 00:14:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think harder.</font>

293
00:14:43,090 --> 00:14:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There isn't a single thing in this world 
 completely irrelevant to you.</font>

294
00:14:50,450 --> 00:14:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home.</font>

295
00:14:52,290 --> 00:14:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back.</font>

296
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:55,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hey, is that Asa-chan?</i></font>

297
00:14:55,050 --> 00:14:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wanna see her!</i></font>

298
00:14:58,380 --> 00:15:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hi there! I'm Motsu.</i></font>

299
00:15:01,790 --> 00:15:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hello to you too.</font>

300
00:15:03,920 --> 00:15:06,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's from the same friend group as Daigo.</font>

301
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:08,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Glad to finally meet you.</i></font>

302
00:15:08,050 --> 00:15:09,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

303
00:15:09,910 --> 00:15:13,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, which do you like better?</font>

304
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

305
00:15:15,150 --> 00:15:16,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The light blue one.</font>

306
00:15:16,190 --> 00:15:17,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Told you so.</i></font>

307
00:15:20,040 --> 00:15:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's it for?</font>

308
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're trying to decide what she should 
wear for her book signing.</i></font>

309
00:15:24,510 --> 00:15:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're doing a book signing?
That's awesome.</font>

310
00:15:27,450 --> 00:15:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Isn't it?</i></font>

311
00:15:28,580 --> 00:15:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all just for show.</font>

312
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>C'mon, you're always so cynical.</i></font>

313
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:34,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about this?</font>

314
00:15:34,850 --> 00:15:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let me see it on.</i></font>

315
00:15:38,890 --> 00:15:43,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think you're supposed 
to step into that one.</i></font>

316
00:15:43,510 --> 00:15:45,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I think you're right.</font>

317
00:15:45,930 --> 00:15:48,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My arms are cramping.</font>

318
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:52,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa, can you zip me up?</font>

319
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Kay.</font>

320
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:55,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You'll need help wearing that.</i></font>

321
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Asa-chan's gotta lend a hand.</i></font>

322
00:15:57,720 --> 00:15:58,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All done.</font>

323
00:15:58,890 --> 00:16:00,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

324
00:16:00,650 --> 00:16:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hey, I like it.</i></font>

325
00:16:02,850 --> 00:16:06,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah? Then maybe I'll go with this.</font>

326
00:16:06,090 --> 00:16:07,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, this book singing...</font>

327
00:16:07,900 --> 00:16:08,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

328
00:16:08,610 --> 00:16:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you be talking in front of
 bunches of people?</font>

329
00:16:10,700 --> 00:16:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I'll say a few words, sure.</font>

330
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:15,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? And you're okay with that?</font>

331
00:16:16,930 --> 00:16:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, since you're 
socially awkward and all.</font>

332
00:16:19,330 --> 00:16:20,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

333
00:16:20,230 --> 00:16:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Actually, you'd be pretty surprised.</i></font>

334
00:16:23,250 --> 00:16:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She gave a great speech at my wedding.</i></font>

335
00:16:26,940 --> 00:16:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Although we ended up splitting.</i></font>

336
00:16:28,850 --> 00:16:33,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm pretty confident I could write 
an even better speech for a divorce.</font>

337
00:16:33,250 --> 00:16:36,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Really? Let's hear it some time!</i></font>

338
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="18">{\an8}<font color="#a6afb8">Makio Koudai Autograph Session</font></font></font></font>

339
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm a huge fan!</font>

340
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks. What's your name?</font>

341
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is "marriage"?</font>

342
00:16:43,260 --> 00:16:44,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wretched!</font>

343
00:16:48,040 --> 00:16:50,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know...</font>

344
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:52,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just, um...</font>

345
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

346
00:16:58,070 --> 00:16:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, let me guess.</i></font>

347
00:16:59,890 --> 00:17:02,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are you getting into teenage angst?</i></font>

348
00:17:02,220 --> 00:17:04,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wanna hear all about it.</i></font>

349
00:17:04,180 --> 00:17:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go again, leeching off
 the energy of the young.</font>

350
00:17:07,290 --> 00:17:09,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is that so bad?</i></font>

351
00:17:09,780 --> 00:17:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

352
00:17:11,490 --> 00:17:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes?</i></font>

353
00:17:13,290 --> 00:17:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno.</font>

354
00:17:15,540 --> 00:17:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is standing out a good thing? 
Or is it a bad thing?</font>

355
00:17:19,060 --> 00:17:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What?</i></font>

356
00:17:20,610 --> 00:17:23,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, I'm not the type 
to really stand out.</font>

357
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:25,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not getting any taller.</font>

358
00:17:25,810 --> 00:17:27,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have a crush on anyone.</font>

359
00:17:27,360 --> 00:17:28,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't write any lyrics.</font>

360
00:17:28,940 --> 00:17:30,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="36"><font color="#6a6452">Curse</font></font></font></font>

361
00:17:29,780 --> 00:17:33,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So for someone like me 
to stand out feels...</font>

362
00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno. I guess it feels wrong.</font>

363
00:17:38,380 --> 00:17:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I'm just not the type.</font>

364
00:17:42,460 --> 00:17:46,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I guess I keep thinking 
it's a bad thing.</font>

365
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:49,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What?! Your </i>type<i>?!</i></font>

366
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who gives a crap about that?</i></font>

367
00:17:52,470 --> 00:17:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez, could you be any more blunt?</font>

368
00:17:54,870 --> 00:17:57,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oops, my bad.</i></font>

369
00:17:57,340 --> 00:18:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was just so silly, 
I couldn't help myself.</i></font>

370
00:18:01,820 --> 00:18:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry, I didn't mean to.</i></font>

371
00:18:03,230 --> 00:18:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But really, who gives
 a hoot about your "type"?</i></font>

372
00:18:08,060 --> 00:18:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You know, I've carried 
a lot of regret about that.</i></font>

373
00:18:12,820 --> 00:18:14,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"The type to be understanding."</i></font>

374
00:18:14,940 --> 00:18:16,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"The type to avoid confrontation."</i></font>

375
00:18:16,910 --> 00:18:19,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"The type to put others first."</i></font>

376
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:21,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"The type to never cry."</i></font>

377
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:23,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I regretted all of those labels.</i></font>

378
00:18:23,690 --> 00:18:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I got so caught up in the labels 
that before I knew it,</i></font>

379
00:18:27,730 --> 00:18:32,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I lost sight of what I actually
 wanted for myself.</i></font>

380
00:18:34,270 --> 00:18:36,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I got off the hamster wheel.</font>

381
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Asa-chan, wanna know what I think?</i></font>

382
00:18:40,410 --> 00:18:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think you should do what you want 
to do, right when you want to do it.</i></font>

383
00:18:45,590 --> 00:18:47,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who cares about the rest?</i></font>

384
00:18:48,970 --> 00:18:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa.</font>

385
00:18:51,210 --> 00:18:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anyone gives you a hard 
time for standing out...</font>

386
00:18:55,180 --> 00:18:56,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give them hell.</font>

387
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that okay?</font>

388
00:19:08,410 --> 00:19:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To give them hell?</font>

389
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, it's not!</i></font>

390
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't listen to her.</i></font>

391
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:15,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's what you always say.</font>

392
00:19:15,270 --> 00:19:18,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah, I'm no novelist. 
Be more expressive.</i></font>

393
00:19:18,100 --> 00:19:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, tear them to pieces.</font>

394
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:22,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't mean like that.</i></font>

395
00:19:22,860 --> 00:19:24,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here! I got it!</font>

396
00:19:24,180 --> 00:19:26,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to sing!</font>

397
00:19:26,060 --> 00:19:27,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Sing?</font>

398
00:19:27,340 --> 00:19:30,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sure! I'm not sure I follow, 
but go for it!</i></font>

399
00:19:33,300 --> 00:19:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The scenery I once saw...</font>

400
00:19:36,630 --> 00:19:41,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}In a daze, shooting stars soon shine...</font>

401
00:19:42,190 --> 00:19:48,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}If only I could watch this forever...</font>

402
00:19:48,700 --> 00:19:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Throw away the past and to the future...</font>

403
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:54,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="18"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474541">Impudent
<font size="12">\hTo be unabashed and brazen</font></font></font></font></font>

404
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:56,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="18"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474541">Inane
<font size="12">To be shallow without knowledge or thought</font></font></font></font></font>

405
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="18"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474541">Evil
<font size="12">To have a twisted, bad heart</font></font></font></font></font>

406
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="18"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474541">Void
<font size="12">To have no value or content</font></font></font></font></font>

407
00:19:53,010 --> 00:19:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}With every meeting, 
I'd like to turn my gaze away</font>

408
00:19:54,350 --> 00:19:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="18"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#474541">Wretched
<font size="12">To have a nasty heart or act on meanness</font></font></font></font></font>

409
00:19:56,250 --> 00:20:00,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're all so forgiving 
of our own contradictions</i></font>

410
00:19:58,950 --> 00:20:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}from my former self, 
from that time and space.</font>

411
00:20:01,290 --> 00:20:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>yet show no sympathy for 
the contradictions of others.</i></font>

412
00:20:05,840 --> 00:20:10,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't realize that 
until much, much later in life.</i></font>

413
00:20:06,550 --> 00:20:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'd like to reach out 
to the sunlight in the dark.</font>

414
00:20:11,610 --> 00:20:16,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}If only I could talk with you right now...</font>

415
00:20:11,820 --> 00:20:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Perhaps we're all like that.</i></font>

416
00:20:15,940 --> 00:20:21,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And perhaps I'll have to grapple 
with that for a long, long time.</i></font>

417
00:20:16,010 --> 00:20:20,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The sunrise seeps into my whole being.</font>

418
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:24,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm free, I'm free.</font>

419
00:20:23,340 --> 00:20:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But maybe...</i></font>

420
00:20:24,450 --> 00:20:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}My eyes are finally beginning to open.</font>

421
00:20:26,220 --> 00:20:27,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just maybe...</i></font>

422
00:20:27,450 --> 00:20:30,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#605a54"><b>Uniform Point Deductions for Female Applicants:
Nitto Medical University Accused of Arbitrary Manipulation</b></font></font></font></font>

423
00:20:27,940 --> 00:20:30,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's not such a bad thing.</i></font>

424
00:20:29,340 --> 00:20:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}If only I could talk with you right now...</font>

425
00:20:33,740 --> 00:20:40,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This day is one to love. It seeps into me.</font>

426
00:20:36,900 --> 00:20:40,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"She's really good."</i></font>

427
00:20:40,950 --> 00:20:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm free, I'm free and flying.</font>

428
00:20:42,290 --> 00:20:43,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"I know."</i></font>

429
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! That's it!</font>

430
00:20:46,060 --> 00:20:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was amazing! Bravo!</i></font>

431
00:20:54,800 --> 00:20:56,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know...</font>

432
00:20:56,340 --> 00:20:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

433
00:20:57,450 --> 00:21:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Without you, Makio-chan, I probably 
wouldn't have joined the band club.</font>

434
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I know I wouldn't have.</font>

435
00:21:05,210 --> 00:21:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think so.</font>

436
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:09,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You made that decision yourself.</font>

437
00:21:09,750 --> 00:21:15,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you would've arrived at that 
no matter who you were with.</font>

438
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what Mom and Dad would have said.</font>

439
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure.</font>

440
00:21:27,540 --> 00:21:28,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe give it some thought.</font>

441
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio-chan...</font>

442
00:21:35,250 --> 00:21:39,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you ever get tired 
of thinking so much?</font>

443
00:21:40,800 --> 00:21:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Seriously, you think way too much.</i></font>

444
00:21:43,520 --> 00:21:44,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to sing!</font>

445
00:21:47,800 --> 00:21:49,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I do.</font>

446
00:21:49,640 --> 00:21:54,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But as long as I'm alive, 
I might as well struggle.</font>

447
00:21:55,630 --> 00:21:58,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't get what you're saying at all!</font>

448
00:21:58,320 --> 00:22:00,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think harder.</font>

449
00:22:01,170 --> 00:22:02,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

450
00:22:02,410 --> 00:22:04,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was mine!</font>

451
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was saving it for later!</font>

452
00:22:07,670 --> 00:22:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oops, sorry, I forgot.</font>

